Personal Blog application for http://www.dalibornasevic.com

- Run following rake task to create session_key and secret for the application

rake config/initializers/session_store.rb 

- Create yaml file config/password.yml with following structure

password:
  username: username
  password: password

- Take a look at config/initializers/constants.rb and set your Last.fm and Twitter usernames, Google Analytics ID, RSS name and description, etc.

- Run cucumber features

cucumber features

- Run specs

spec spec --options spec/spec.opts
